          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Agriculture Risk Coverage Improvement and Innovation Act of 2018 </b></p> <p>This bill reauthorizes and modifies Department of Agriculture commodity programs, including the Agriculture Risk Coverage Program and the Price Loss Coverage Program. The bill modifies payment calculations, coverage levels, and other requirements of the Agriculture Risk Coverage Program.</p>]]></text>
